==English==

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɑː(r)tɪkəl|-ɑː(r)tɪkəl]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
<!-- these defs are definitely in the wrong order! -->
# (''grammar'') a word, a type of [[determiner]], that specifies or limits the following noun. (''a'', ''an'', or ''the'' in English)
# a member of a group or class, e.g. ''article of clothing''.
# an object.
# a section of a legal document, bylaws, etc.
# a story, report, or opinion piece in a newspaper, magazine, or journal.
# (''derogatory'') a person.
# {{vulgar}} A wench. A prime article. A handsome girl.  She's a prime article (''whip slang''), she's a devilish good piece, a hell of a ''goer''.

